{"tid":2153060,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"是你N賓 無人車廂裡放針","createTime":"2020-08-12T10:22:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-12T18:18:07.000Z","uid":343520,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"68aee019ab8aae5e0abc49368ba5f589d159c625","tid":2153060,"uid":343520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T10:22:30.000Z","msg":"絕對空虛<br />\n<br />\n作詞：我&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;作曲：水谷公生<br />\n<br />\n助法子泰博做勢　兆健與錦滿答謝你<br />\n每次寫歌讚美　熱血是很感激<br />\n<br />\n立法會裡正在播　舊日你喜歡改的歌<br />\n泰博的心已碎　獨跌坐失意裡<br />\n閉起眼睛想過去<br />\n<br />\n是你N賓 (是你N賓)<br />\n無人車廂裡放針　<br />\n望見N賓 (望見N賓)<br />\n全城搭客很驚怕<br />\n仍然在插你！ 全力插你！ 插你是永沒年期！<br />\n仍然在插你！ 如從沒插你！ 世界頓變了乏味！<br />\n<br />\n但願你別放針　但願阿sir會肯<br />\n快點拉你 (快點拉你)"},{"pid":"5854b82f1337f9f59a4607347f4018d41e61bab5","tid":2153060,"uid":241543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T10:23:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86d445bd4e446765c9921ef6ac959e22b1d7a5d0","tid":2153060,"uid":343520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5854b82f1337f9f59a4607347f4018d41e61bab5","tid":2153060,"uid":241543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T10:23:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T10:26:06.000Z","msg":"Ching你都幾癲 次次一出po就來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d9fd6188a1a720260c481b49841e93e1b78442b","tid":2153060,"uid":72497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T10:39:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df34eb9157ea98cb9fff2978e1cac7dda7b6740b","tid":2153060,"uid":234509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86d445bd4e446765c9921ef6ac959e22b1d7a5d0","tid":2153060,"uid":343520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5854b82f1337f9f59a4607347f4018d41e61bab5","tid":2153060,"uid":241543,"like":0,"d